description: Demolition of existing buildings. Erection of a mixed-use development up to 17-storeys (three-storey podium with 14-storey, 10-storey, 6-storey and 5-storey buildings above) to provide car showroom and workshop (with ancillary caf) (Sui Generis) on ground, first and second floors and 173 residential units (Use Class C3) comprising market and affordable housing above with access to landscaped amenity deck.  A basement car park would provide residents with 87 vehicle and 184 cycle parking spaces. Within the ground floor would be 29 parking spaces for customers. Public realm improvements to Bridges Court and York Road.
